        <updateDate>2007-07-26T18:31:15Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Saving Families First Alternative Minimum Tax Relief Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow: (1) the tax deduction for personal exemptions in determining the alternative minimum taxable income of individual taxpayers; and (2) an inflation adjustment for alternative minimum tax exemption and phaseout amounts for individual taxpayers beginning after 2007. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
